## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **aprocitentan Tryvio 2024** = first FDA-approved endothelin RA (ETA + ETB) for RH (resistant hypertension). PRECISION trial paradigm — 3+ drug RH 환자 mean -3.8/-3.9 mmHg vs placebo at week 4. quantum-VQE 의 ETA/ETB dual-pocket fit.
2. **zilebesiran (Alnylam + Roche, research)** = first AGT (angiotensinogen) siRNA. KARDIA-1 (Phase 2) + KARDIA-2 (combo) 2024 결과 quarterly SC ~10-20 mmHg sustained. 양자-VQE 의 oligonucleotide-Ago2-RISC modeling fit. paradigm shift = "biannual" injection HTN.
3. **finerenone Kerendia 2021** = first non-steroidal MR antagonist FDA. CKD + T2D 적응증 — FIDELIO-DKD + FIGARO-DKD trial. spironolactone gynecomastia/hyperK 부작용 회피. quantum-VQE 의 non-steroidal MR pocket leverage.
4. **baxdrostat + lorundrostat (research, Phase 3)** = aldosterone synthase CYP11B2 inhibitor — RH + primary aldosteronism. CYP11B1 cortisol selectivity 가 핵심 challenge. quantum-VQE 의 P450 active-site selectivity fit.
5. **thiazide chlorthalidone (1958+) + hydrochlorothiazide (1959+) + indapamide** = 65년 1L HTN 표준. ALLHAT 2002 chlorthalidone first-line confirm. K-loss + glucose intolerance + uric acid 부작용 인식 + indapamide 가 metabolic-neutral 우위.
6. **ACE-i lisinopril + enalapril + ramipril (1981+)** = HOPE 1999 ramipril CV mortality reduce + 만성 nephroprotection paradigm. K-elevation + cough (bradykinin) + angioedema 한계 → ARB switch.
7. **ARB losartan 1995 + valsartan + telmisartan + candesartan + olmesartan** = ACE-i intolerant 1L equivalent. 양자-VQE 의 AT1 pocket — telmisartan PPARγ partial agonist metabolic 우위.
8. **CCB amlodipine (1987+) + nifedipine + diltiazem + verapamil** = 1L HTN — DHP vs non-DHP 분리. amlodipine + ARB combo (e.g., olmesartan/amlodipine) = 만성 fixed-dose paradigm.
9. **β-blocker = no longer 1L per ESC 2018** — 만성 secondary 적응증 (HF + post-MI + AF rate-control + migraine). atenolol 가 outcome trials 에서 stroke prevention 열등 = 1L 추락 contributor.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HTN 임상 의미 한정. PRECISION + KARDIA-1+2 + STEP + ACCORD + HOPE-3 trial paradigm 은 임상 source 로만 인용.

